11. Be2{ In order to prepare the development of White's king's knight to  f3 ; after an exchange, White is then ready to recapture with the bishop. }( 11.Nxd5 Nxd5 12.Qxd5 { spells trouble since after }12...Bb4+ 13.Bd2 Bxd2+ 14.Qxd2 Qf6 { , }{ White has to defend against the threat ... Rb8xb2  followed by a discovered check on  d3 . That will give us the time to castle and take advantage of White's dormant kingside pieces and 'centralized' king. } )
