9. Bxc4
9. O-O( { Starting with }9...cxd4 { would give White the additional option of }10.Bb5 { . } )
10. O-O
10. cxd4
11. exd4
11. Nc6{ Black is slightly better, as development has been fully completed and White has nothing to show for the isolated d-pawn. }
