18. g3
18. Qf6{ Having provoked the weakening  g2 - g3  move, we happily return to the square we wanted to go to in the first place. The new targets are  f5  and  b2 . }
19. Nxd5
19. cxd5
20. Qxd5( { Capturing a second pawn. We should focus on development here, and that means }20...Qxb2+ 21.Qd2 { would be a mistake. } )
20. Nc6{ We bring our rooks to the center next and should have little worries! }
