16. Nbd7{ Opening preparation runs deep these days! With the engine, initially, giving White a plus, it would have been easy to stop our analysis after  16.Bxd3 , but we will not. As it transpires, Black still has compensation here, as it is difficult for White to stabilize the position. }
17. Bc4( { Stopping the  f6 -knight from jumping to  d5 , which is what would happen after }17.Re1 { . } )
