10. Nfd7( { The endgame after }10...Qxd1 11.Nxd1 Nfd7 12.e4 Be6 13.Nde3 { is pretty lousy. Instead, the text move aims to win }{ back the  e5 -pawn slowly, with moves like ... Bf5 - e6xc4 , or ... Qd8 - e7 . } )
11. f4
11. Be6
12. e4
12. Qe7{ This transposes to the  11.e4 line . }
