25. Rxc6
26. Rxd5
26. h5{ This endgame is an easy draw even if we lose both a-pawns, which is not a given. White's advantage of bishop versus two pawns on the kingside will not be enough to win. If this assessment is not that clear to you, do investigate this position a bit further and you will find there is nothing to fear! }
