16. Nc5
16. Nxc5( { Simplest, but }16...Nxe5!? { can be considered as well since }17.Nxb7 { ( }17.Bd4 Bxf1 18.Bxe5 Bxg2 19.Rg1 f6 { )   }17...Bg7 { gives Black an active game, and   }17.Bd4 { works tactically after }17...Bxf1 18.Bxe5 Bxg2 19.Rg1 f6! { , when Black is doing very well. } )
17. Bxc5
