14. Nc3{ We have been following the game Carlsen-Harikrishna, Aimchess rapid 2022. That game was eventually drawn, but the opening can rightly be called a success for Hari. Here we will deviate. }
14. b4( 14...O-O { , which is what Hari played, is fine as well, but the text move is even stronger. } )
15. Na4
15. Qb8{ Black's advantage is already quite serious, and ... Bd7 - b5  is an annoying threat. }
