13. a4
13. Nbd7{ If allowed, we will play ... Nd7 - b6  next and establish our knight on  d5 . }( { In case of }14.a5 { , we will play }14...Ne4 { instead, and bring }{ our  d7 -knight over to  f6 . }{ We have excellent play. } )( { Note that trying to prevent  14.a5 , with }13...a5 14.Bd2 Nbd7 { runs into }15.Ng5! { , which is slightly uncomfortable. }{ It's hard to protect  f7 , as }15...Nb6 16.Bxf7+ Rxf7 17.Nxf7 { loses on the spot. } )
