11. Qc2( { Already an inaccuracy, which went unpunished in the blitz game Shankland-Giri, Almaty 2022. White should probably make a neutral move like }11.Kg2 { or }11.Bd2 { , but there can be no talk of any advantage whatsoever. } )
11. dxc4
12. Bxc4
12. Ng4{ That h-file is surely coming in handy! The remainder of the line is very pretty. }
13. h4
