16. f3
16. Nf8( { Black is in fine shape. We will regroup with ... Qh2 - c7  and ... Nf8 - e6  next, while }17.e4?! dxe4 { allows us to take }{ on  d4  next move. } )( { The engine proposes }17.Qa4 Qc7 18.Bd3 Ne6 19.Ne2 { , }{ attacking the  a5 -pawn, }19...Ra8 { and with ... b7 - b5  coming and still up a pawn, chances are approximately equal. My materialistic self would always take Black though. } )
