9. Bg2
9. Bb4
10. O-O
10. Bxc3{ This is the idea. We voluntarily give up on the bishop pair in order to play on the light squares. }
11. bxc3
11. Qa5
12. Bd2
12. O-O{ We have slightly the better of it in what is otherwise an approximately equal position. }
