11. e6
12. Be2
12. Bd6
13. Bg5{ Exchanging on  d6  is admitting the opening phase has not been a success. }
13. Ne7( { The position is equal. After }14.Qxd7 Nxd7 { , White's bishop pair isn't very effective and   }14.Qb3 { is well met with }14...Ne4!  )
