11. Bc7+{ Without this move, Black would just be winning. }
11. Qe7( { Looking for an adventure? In that case }11...Ne3 12.Bxd8 Rxd8 { may be something for you. It may not be entirely correct, but certainly Black has compensation for the queen. } )
12. Bxd5
12. Nb4( 12...Bxc2 { is possible too. } )
13. Bxb7
13. Nxc2+
14. Kd2
14. Kd7{ Not just attacking the bishop on  c7 , but also unpinning the queen, which makes it possible to take on  c5  next move. }
15. Bf4
15. Qxc5
16. Bxa8
16. Nxa1( { It's time to end the line. We are in good shape, as the sample line }17.Be4 g5!? 18.Bg3 Qa5+ 19.Kd1 Be6 { shows. } )
