7. Be6{ A cool response, bringing yet another piece into the game and threatening ... Nf6 - d5 . }
8. dxe7
8. Bxe7
9. Nd6+
9. Kf8{ As good a moment as any to end the line. Yes, our last move prevents us from ever castling again, but the extra pawn and huge lead in development certainly more than make up for it! Black is already winning. }
