2. c5( { Simply hitting the center. }2...f6 { is probably the strongest and most principled response but also requires some knowledge of concrete lines. We aren't going to face  2.Bg5  all that much in our lifetime and therefore I prefer a more practical and healthy choice that we can also whip out half a year from now, without remembering much. What's more, here too, it ain't much fun for White. } )
