2. Nf6( 3.Nf3 { would now transpose to the chapter on the  3rd Move Sidelines . } )
3. Bg5( { Played on occasion by both Carlsen and Aronian. It is essentially a transposition to the Trompowsky, which arises after   }1.d4 Nf6 2.Bg5 d5 { and now }3.c3 { . } )
