5. e3{ Allowing the capture on  f4  is also fairly typical these days, but tempi does count and White has played  a2 - a3 , which makes this not a very critical version of the better-known lines. }
5. O-O
6. Nbd2
6. b6{ Preparing to exchange the light-squared bishops with ... Bc8 - a6 . We are comfortably equal. }
